            <lg xml:id="TK202">
<l>tīyavai tīya payattalāṟ ṟīyavai</l>
<l>tīyiṉu mañcap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Because evil produces evil, therefore should evil be feared more than fire.</l>
